74
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:23,660
Hehe, saatnya menggoreng ikan.

75
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,930
Duri Neraka.

76
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:48,500
Teknik roh ke-5, Meteor Phoenix.

77
00:07:55,230 --> 00:07:57,400
Teknik roh ke-6,
Serangan Phoenix Menembus Awan.

78
00:07:59,930 --> 00:08:01,560
Terimalah kematianmu, Harimau Iblis!

79
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:16,730
Semua karena dia,
hanya perlu mengatasinya.

80
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,460
Tang San, hati-hati!

81
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:22,630
